{"tid":96551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【玻璃心】小米副總裁「健康問題」辭職即投fb 網民：你呃人","createTime":"2017-01-27T02:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T03:57:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7a8db67098aa505262320f8c715b19e29d72e2","tid":96551,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170126/280pix/1485420593_e65d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170126%2F280pix%2F1485420593_e65d.jpg&h=9fe6ee1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小米全球副總裁巴拉（Hugo Barra）日前以北京的「異常環境影響健康」辭職，讓不少內地網民覺得不捨，沒想到fb創辦人朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）宣佈，巴拉將會加入Facebook的虛擬現實團隊，這讓不少內地網民傷心：「看來身體沒問題！」「小米很尷尬！」<br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格在fb上公佈巴拉加入的消息，指目前仍在中國的巴拉，將會加入虛擬現實團隊，當中包括新近收購的Oculus團隊，而巴拉稱虛擬現實領域工作是他一直以來的夢想，他更稱從小米CEO雷軍身上「學到一點」，就是將突破性技術推廣至大眾是最重要的。<br />\n<br />\n對於巴拉聲稱，「最近幾年居住在（北京）這種特殊的環境中，對我的生活造成了很大的損害，並已經影響到我的健康」，但馬上轉職fb，引發很多內地網民不滿：「fb還能治病，健康問題沒了！」「健康問題幾天就能解決！」「這屬於心理健康欠佳&hellip;&hellip;」「霧霾：這鍋我不背！」<br />\n<br />\n從Google到小米，從小米到fb，不少網民都稱內地留不住人才，「這是一個明智的選擇」，「有種迫不及待的意味，小米此刻表示很尷尬！」「現在立刻就能去臉書，這是有本事的人！」<br />\n<br />\n新浪科技<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56226867&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56226867%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170126&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2B5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=498d0a62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56226867%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170126&h=3c4a8d90\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56226867&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170126</a>"},{"pid":"c2fe3550dc4555e9b4dae18b8ee2ee7043ee5fe6","tid":96551,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be8e3fe3cb470f4dacf98a91eb189445d009dec","tid":96551,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21904980cc41a128b3be2be7b99499737c2b69a8","tid":96551,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf3741bbf5d0d531b139f312739aeee2eab1de9","tid":96551,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3592935c49be40bbea3413c638379b03b9a6db3","tid":96551,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"大陸人又玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地咪話左天氣差所以走"}]}